Package: novena-bluetooth-reset
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libbluetooth3
Description: Reset Bluetooth when Config button is pressed
 Bluetooth is buggy on Novena.  It can go away after several hours idle.
 Monitor the front User button, and bring HCI down and up and it is pressed.
